{"tid":1127190,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"晚清底層社會老照片：落後面貌不忍直視","createTime":"2019-04-27T02:28:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-27T06:14:52.000Z","uid":49263,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"50ad34da9e68f307ef87d664a9321b184c45c5d5","tid":1127190,"uid":49263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T02:28:37.000Z","msg":"1903年-1904年，美國地質學家魯夫斯&middot;哈維&middot;薩金特（R. Harvey Sargent）受卡內基研究所資助，在中國進行了一次科學考察。考察過程中，他用相機記錄了所到之處的社會面貌。<br />\n<br />\n　　<img src=\"http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190421/d7c09d264d19488c8c78cffbd94465e0.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com%2Fimages%2F20190421%2Fd7c09d264d19488c8c78cffbd94465e0.jpeg&h=fb2635cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n　　農民在磨面。<br />\n<br />\n　　<img src=\"http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190421/ebf44fa536eb4ef8a4410ad1bae820f5.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com%2Fimages%2F20190421%2Febf44fa536eb4ef8a4410ad1bae820f5.jpeg&h=7d7f701c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n　　官衙內景。<br />\n<br />\n　　薩金特一行乘船抵達山東省，經直隸、北京前往山西，再跨越黃河進入陝西，由陝西南下秦嶺，繼而沿長江東下。數千公里的行程，已經深入到了清朝的腹地，足以讓這一群外國人了解清朝的真實狀況。<br />\n<br />\n　　<img src=\"http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190421/e42f0d204318425198c2c9f814156652.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com%2Fimages%2F20190421%2Fe42f0d204318425198c2c9f814156652.jpeg&h=fd90ba8f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n　　農民好奇地圍觀外國人拍照。<br />\n<br />\n　　薩金特的這些影像最終以《China：Exploring the Interior》（《探索中國內部》）的名稱流傳於世。由此名稱可以猜測，薩金特的到來可能有蒐集清朝情報的目的。<br />\n<br />\n　　<img src=\"http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190421/70f10abd6b074c9899a7f5b651ac6f6d.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com%2Fimages%2F20190421%2F70f10abd6b074c9899a7f5b651ac6f6d.jpeg&h=eef15972&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n　　騎驢出門的婦女。<br />\n<br />\n　　晚清在華拍攝的外國攝影師比較多，但大多集中在沿海城市，像薩金特這樣深入閉塞的農村、記錄底層社會影像的，並不多見。因此，薩金特的作品具有別樣的價值，如今已成為珍貴的第一手史料。<br />\n<br />\n　　<img src=\"http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190421/5475810921954606a8151f16ceaa8183.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com%2Fimages%2F20190421%2F5475810921954606a8151f16ceaa8183.jpeg&h=e77bd9f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n　　在小溪邊洗衣服的婦女。<br />\n<br />\n　　薩金特雖然是業餘攝影師，但他的作品捕捉到了晚清農村的特點和環境，正是一個日益沒落的帝國的真實寫照。我們在教科書中學到晚清的中國社會很落後、很貧窮，這種落後貧窮是一種什麼狀態呢？這些照片直觀地呈現了出來。<br />\n<br />\n　　<img src=\"http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190421/33bfe935f86a4c8892045ac0a3b97a3c.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com%2Fimages%2F20190421%2F33bfe935f86a4c8892045ac0a3b97a3c.jpeg&h=df0e32ff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n　　山西，圍觀薩金特一行的農民。<br />\n<br />\n　　這些農村深處內陸，百姓過著傳統的自給自足的小農生活，與外界交流很少。別說沒見過外國人了，就是大城市來的本國同胞都寥寥可數。所以，當薩金特等人來此，他們難免對金發碧眼的洋人產生濃厚的好奇心。<br />\n<br />\n　　<img src=\"http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190421/68ed30bcbd23456384e7c077474a39a8.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com%2Fimages%2F20190421%2F68ed30bcbd23456384e7c077474a39a8.jpeg&h=d9de0e47&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n　　一群農民強勢圍觀薩金特一行。薩金特說：&ldquo;在我們到達這裡的最初20分鐘內，山上沒有一個人。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n　　<img src=\"http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190421/d48f50e94a244b07898b61653421a366.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com%2Fimages%2F20190421%2Fd48f50e94a244b07898b61653421a366.jpeg&h=25872465&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n　　山西汾州，圍觀薩金特一行的婦女兒童。<br />\n<br />\n　　<img src=\"http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190421/195014d1f35f4c959612d9fd4662c57f.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com%2Fimages%2F20190421%2F195014d1f35f4c959612d9fd4662c57f.jpeg&h=c30e5871&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n　　砍柴的農民。農民上山砍柴，然後搬回家自用或者出售，薩金特說大約10磅重的柴能賣一美分。<br />\n<br />\n　　<img src=\"http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20190421/deebaee240de4a52abcc67b4979cf1b5.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com%2Fimages%2F20190421%2Fdeebaee240de4a52abcc67b4979cf1b5.jpeg&h=fc220c6b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n　　建造新房子。<br />\n<br />\n　　薩金特到來之際，清朝剛剛經歷庚子之亂，慈禧太后痛定思痛，決定實施新政，開啟一場全面的改革。實施新政處處需要錢，錢從何來呢？官府就在農村加捐加賦，薅農民的羊毛，這加速了農村的凋敝。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nsource:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.backchina.com/forum.php?mod=viewthread&amp;tid=1660370&amp;extra=page%3D1&amp;mobile=2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.backchina.com%2Fforum.php%3Fmod%3Dviewthread%26tid%3D1660370%26extra%3Dpage%253D1%26mobile%3D2&d=wHiIeFeeqtLxwJ75m5qcs8tNvD6oN5AbUd1%2F%2Bp%2BoAYU%3D&h=1fe1f43e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.backchina.com/forum.php?mod=viewthread&amp;tid=1660370&amp;extra=page%3D1&amp;mobile=2</a>"},{"pid":"1518a3da0511891e59873eb8f45f45e6a274dabe","tid":1127190,"uid":40470,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T02:30:26.000Z","msg":"唔係好差姐"},{"pid":"c2c21b86d9a1b9f7a585b89dcec52f719948c91b","tid":1127190,"uid":46042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T02:33:22.000Z","msg":"癲"},{"pid":"6f837a76da5288b9e15d749aed572f5896d36dfa","tid":1127190,"uid":46042,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T02:34:36.000Z","msg":"有衫著重想點"},{"pid":"d6d4ef5e88c844045b2a2a4fb96d1618ec446e9f","tid":1127190,"uid":48234,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T02:37:28.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">晚共同晚清真係好撚似</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64ea56f89c4dd7e91d8cf5440b71fa3565a87cc7","tid":1127190,"uid":136776,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T02:37:36.000Z","msg":"事實證明錢真係可以改變樣子<br />\n上面張農民圖真係分唔到邊個打邊個<br />\n好似全部都係換臉咁"},{"pid":"d4e2ee39832f1d7ff859a7e053ccfaa708f06cb0","tid":1127190,"uid":67771,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T02:39:18.000Z","msg":"同而家差唔多"},{"pid":"61a49807b4ed406088f718e474287429282b1ea0","tid":1127190,"uid":162713,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T02:41:53.000Z","msg":"其實個個都有衫褲著 <br />\n呢條村都唔算太差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3e53a1842af30ed6984370ea3315e14381c6ba4","tid":1127190,"uid":174601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T02:44:42.000Z","msg":"佢地好撚窮<br />\n又唔識字<br />\n<br />\n但係佢地唔洗住劏房<br />\n身體又強壯"},{"pid":"4d4d29ce17444c1883adf84cdb79ef4a75fc5d17","tid":1127190,"uid":57023,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T02:49:24.000Z","msg":"唔好講晩清, 就算康雍乾所謂盛世都係吹出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c910c2230ce021398989f60406b521f94b8c00d5","tid":1127190,"uid":25794,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T02:49:24.000Z","msg":"第一張相話磨面 <br />\n我係咁睇果幾條友邊個磨緊面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ada3c4b76a439417a57911c0d3e4b5e254a67693","tid":1127190,"uid":108467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T02:55:19.000Z","msg":"記得有張gif係，班外國人派嘢俾中國細路，啲細路好似狗咁執嗰啲嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52c153d642966ff55ea50003275e247ca9d4fa13","tid":1127190,"uid":40862,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"6f837a76da5288b9e15d749aed572f5896d36dfa","tid":1127190,"uid":46042,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T02:34:36.000Z","msg":"有衫著重想點"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T02:57:17.000Z","msg":"呢個真睇睇韓國，仲嚇人。"},{"pid":"5d1de810ba2cd4cf70c4ffd1f4e0735f0602fb34","tid":1127190,"uid":164920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T03:03:03.000Z","msg":"得啲on9大中華膠先會吹奏中國古代皇朝幾撚巴閉"},{"pid":"e4fe9761ea5524e97d742834f9b068bd8732d900","tid":1127190,"uid":22736,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T03:25:32.000Z","msg":"好過共黨60年代果時"},{"pid":"8ebfd799e5399ce262747f6c9a83d48ab693497f","tid":1127190,"uid":49263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T03:59:34.000Z","msg":"好想知南宋個社會環境係點"},{"pid":"0b6d917c20c124e8f14d3afd2b8e88f0d901f156","tid":1127190,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T05:02:03.000Z","msg":"對對對，講滿州話以至普通話的確係落後"},{"pid":"d2dbe7cb7cdf891901eaca5086c36884774d187f","tid":1127190,"uid":79442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T05:06:51.000Z","msg":"拎末期黎比又差d,<br />\n每個朝代末年都pk架啦"},{"pid":"07e335f592ec7fed79a33ed4d1f61bdcac6055ae","tid":1127190,"uid":60508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T06:14:52.000Z","msg":"係咪有外國人去過明朝，講過話明朝都ok？"}]}